  <steps>
    <step order="1">Read ADR-033 (canonical architecture) + spec FR-07/08/09/10/11/12/13 + NFR-03 to ground guide scope.</step>
    <step order="2">Read the as-built engine + 3 wrappers + `communicationApi.ts` to extract the actual prop API surfaces (what shipped, not what spec proposed — these may differ on detail).</step>
